  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338520/extras/c84ae6bbc02ab79f6c394a16d9cccc1c.avif?t=1606096389\" width=500 height=320 /></span><br>Bouncy Cat is hungry for fish and wants to play with yarn. <br>Bounce and shrink across 60 levels to help him achieve his dreams.<br>Collect Yarn to obtain stylish hats.<br>Each level has 5 objectives, enhancing replayability.<br>A game that's perfect for speedrunners.<br><br>Controls<br><br>Grow: Left Click/Space<br><br>Shrink: Right Click/Shift<br><br>Camera: Mouse Movement<br><br>Movement: WASD<br><br>Reset: R<br><br>Menu: Escape<br><br><br><br>Level Objectives<br><br>1. Beat level by collecting the fish<br><br>2. Beat the level and collect the yarn<br><br>3.  Beat the level under the par time <br><br>4. Beat the level under the par time and collect the yarn<br><br>5. Beat the expert time",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338520/extras/c84ae6bbc02ab79f6c394a16d9cccc1c.avif?t=1606096389\" width=500 height=320 /></span><br>Bouncy Cat is hungry for fish and wants to play with yarn. <br>Bounce and shrink across 60 levels to help him achieve his dreams.<br>Collect Yarn to obtain stylish hats.<br>Each level has 5 objectives, enhancing replayability.<br>A game that's perfect for speedrunners.<br><br>Controls<br><br>Grow: Left Click/Space<br><br>Shrink: Right Click/Shift<br><br>Camera: Mouse Movement<br><br>Movement: WASD<br><br>Reset: R<br><br>Menu: Escape<br><br><br><br>Level Objectives<br><br>1. Beat level by collecting the fish<br><br>2. Beat the level and collect the yarn<br><br>3.  Beat the level under the par time <br><br>4. Beat the level under the par time and collect the yarn<br><br>5. Beat the expert time",
